txt.en: 'There are still more Orcs residing beneath the Wastes. If you find yourself within the maggot tunnels, defeat the Orcs you see. They must not be allowed to attack the Host of the West.'
The Enemy can be found within the caverns of Skoironk.\n\nYou should defeat enemies within Skoironk.
You have defeated many enemies within the caverns of Skoironk and have helped the Rangers of Ithilien a great deal.
Thurindol believes that many more Orcs hide and wait for the Host of the West within the Maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk.
